<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> <a href="/wiki/Joseph_Conrad" title="Joseph Conrad">Joseph Conrad</a>'s <a href="/wiki/Heart_of_Darkness" title="Heart of Darkness">Heart of Darkness</a> was published in 1902 and <a href="/wiki/T.S_Eliot" title="T.S Eliot" class="mw-redirect">T.S Eliot</a>'s <a href="/wiki/The_Wasteland" title="The Wasteland" class="mw-redirect">The Wasteland</a> in 1922. See linked pages and their sources for corroboration of their importance as Modernist artefacts.</li>
